text.tspan: MedMan is a B2B Marketplace for Medicines and
Healthcare products. It is a collaborative trade platform that
enables business entities to discover products at better rates,
transact and get them delivered anywhere in India.
MedMan provides a digital bridge between retailers
and suppliers and is enabled to deliver all over India.
